AVIAN INFLUENZA (91): THAILAND (PREVENTION), VIET NAM
*****************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
In this update:
[1] Thailand - prevention
[2] Viet Nam (Ninh Binh, Bac Ninh)
